{"type":"message","id":"ddc9e05d","parentId":"f4959495","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:43:44.985Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_icms1y9kusv0_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5090\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3310\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 084315 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next critical step, but I need to first understand the pulse log structure to build a classifier that can identify invariants vs variants across sessions.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"brisk-slug","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5090\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3310\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 084315 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next critical step, but I need to first understand the pulse log structure to build a classifier that can identify invariants vs variants across sessions.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774356224983}}
